init_text: Humans once wielded formidable magical power. But with over 7 billion of us on the planet now, Mana has spread far too thinly to have any effect. When hostile aliens reduce humanity to a mere fraction, the survivors discover an old power has begun to reawaken once again.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The city of Atlanta has become a battleground for the survival of the human race.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Now, three young students discover a secret that may change everything...

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The Mana Cave is the original source of all Mana.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The Mana Cave is the key to victory.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The cave is protected by a magical seal that only allows people of the purest hearts and truest intentions to enter.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: And those who have made it inside have never returned.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Some believe the cave is a myth.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: This is what the three friends have set out to do.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They succeed in entering the cave.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: But they quickly discover that the cave is more than what it seems.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: But once they enter the cave, things change.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Soon they find themselves in a mysterious place and realize they are not alone.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The friends find themselves at a place known as the Throne Room.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: But then, the throne begins to shake and a light fills the room.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It said, "I am the guardian of this cave.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "You are not here to guard the cave?"

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Without hesitation, one of the friends stepped forward.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The other two friends were shocked and scared.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They knew this was a bad idea.
